Type: Package
Package: psycModel
Title: Integrated Toolkit for Psychological Analysis and Modeling in R
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Jason", family = "Moy", role = c("aut",
        "cre"), email = "jasonmoy28@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID =
        "0000-0001-8795-3311"))
Description: A beginner-friendly R package for modeling in psychology
        or related field. It allows fitting models, plotting, checking
        goodness of fit, and model assumption violations all in one
        place. It also produces beautiful and easy-to-read output.
